---
layout: base.njk
htmlClass: "home"
preload: "portrait-tall.jpg"
title: "Home"
order: 0
---

{% set sortedWork = work | sortByYear %}

<section class="home" id="home">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="columns mb-10xl">
      <div class="columns-12 md:columns-7">
        {% set intro = "For more than 15 years, I've helped agencies, publishers, and nonprofits create accessible websites, corporate reports, and media platforms. As an independent developer, I partner with client teams to build polished user interfaces that are fast, reliable, and easy to use." %}

        <h1 class="type-xlarge flex flex-wrap">
          {%- for char in intro.split(' ') -%}
            <span class="overflow-hidden flex"><i data-reveal data-stagger="15">{{ char }}</i>&nbsp;</span>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div class="columns-6 md:columns-5 lg:columns-2" data-reveal="clipy" data-delay="300">
        {% img "portrait-tall.jpg", "", "", "eager" %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="columns my-10xl --row-gap-5xl">
      <div class="columns-10 md:columns-4">
        <h2 data-reveal data-delay="300">Work</h2>
        {% set description1 = "Nunc eleifend tincidunt mi, id sollicitudin justo luctus id. Integer et diam sit amet leo porttitor fermentum. Ut ac turpis vitae quam ultrices vehicula eu eu velit. Nullam sed euismod diam. Suspendisse malesuada vestibulum tortor, eu accumsan leo pretium id. Integer placerat nulla vitae lacus ullamcorper, ac tincidunt elit varius. Sed convallis mauris et massa interdum faucibus." %}
        {% set description2 ="Sed gravida at urna a posuere. Sed non diam vitae velit rutrum venenatis. In ut libero sem. Phasellus vitae finibus quam, a tempus quam. Fusce auctor, lorem et eleifend laoreet, sapien nisi porta lacus, non aliquet mi risus eget mi. Cras pellentesque neque a ex vestibulum, sed pharetra mi porta. Suspendisse nec pretium erat, sit amet sollicitudin lacus. Vivamus augue est, fermentum at libero et, viverra egestas quam. Sed faucibus dui at enim ultricies, a condimentum arcu faucibus. Pellentesque interdum et orci vitae elementum. Integer tincidunt eu ante eget dapibus." %}

        <p class="flex flex-wrap">
        {%- for char in description1.split(' ') -%}
          <span class="overflow-hidden flex"><i data-reveal data-stagger="5">{{ char }}</i>&nbsp;</span>
        {%- endfor -%}
        </p>

        <p class="flex flex-wrap">
        {%- for char in description2.split(' ') -%}
          <span class="overflow-hidden flex"><i data-reveal data-stagger="5">{{ char }}</i>&nbsp;</span>
        {%- endfor -%}
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="columns-6 md:columns-3 md:ml-3">
        <h2 data-reveal data-delay="200">Services</h2>
        <ul>
          <li data-reveal>Sustainability Reports</li>
          <li data-reveal>Corporate Communications</li>
          <li data-reveal>Annual Reports</li>
          <li data-reveal>Investor Relations Websites</li>
          <li data-reveal>Microsites & Campaign Sites</li>

          <li data-reveal>Static Site Architecture</li>
          <li data-reveal>Data Visualization</li>
          <li data-reveal>Bespoke Animations</li>
          <li data-reveal>Microinteractions</li>
          <li data-reveal>Interactive Charts & Tables</li>
          <li data-reveal>Accessibility (WCAG)</li>
          <li data-reveal>Performance Optimization</li>
          <li data-reveal>Analytics & Measurement</li>
          <li data-reveal>Technical Consulting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="columns-4 md:columns-2 ml-1 md:ml-zero">
        <h2 data-reveal data-delay="200">Technologies</h2>
        <ul>
          <li data-reveal>11ty</li>
          <li data-reveal>Jekyll</li>
          <li data-reveal>HTML</li>
          <li data-reveal>CSS / SCSS</li>
          <li data-reveal>JavaScript</li>
          <li data-reveal>Node.js</li>
          <li data-reveal>Nunjucks</li>
          <li data-reveal>Liquid</li>
          <li data-reveal>Jinja2</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="columns md:columns-6 lg:columns-4 justify-center my-10xl">
      {% set i = 0 %}

      {% for page in collections.showcase %}
        {% if page.data.client in["United","NRMP","FNIH","AXIOS","NYU","Dominion Energy"] %}
          {% set i = i + 1 %}
          <div data-reveal data-stagger="250" class="card card--logo">
            {%- set svg_url = 'company/' ~ page.data.client | slugify ~ '.svg' -%}
            <div class="card__index">{{ i < 10 and '0' + i or i }}.</div>

            <a href="{{ page.url | url }}">
              <h2>{{page.data.long or page.data.client}}</h2>
              {% svg svg_url, "" %}
            </a>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
      <div>
        <a class="button" href="{{ "/showcase/" | url }}">Explore Case Studies {% svg "arrow.svg" %}</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <ul class="home__work my-10xl" role="table" aria-label="Work">
      <li data-reveal class="columns font-black" role="row">
        <span role="columnheader" class="columns-6 md:columns-6 lg:columns-7 border-b-1">Client</span>
        <span role="columnheader" class="columns-6 md:columns-5 lg:columns-3 border-b-1">Website</span>
        <span role="columnheader" class="md:columns-1 lg:columns-2 border-b-1">Year</span>
      </li>

      {%- for item in work -%}
        <li data-reveal data-stagger="15" class="columns" role="row">
          <span role="rowheader" class="columns-6 md:columns-6 lg:columns-7">{{item.client}}</span>
          <span role="cell" class="columns-6 md:columns-5 lg:columns-3">{{item.project}}</span>
          <span role="cell" class="md:columns-1 lg:columns-2">{{item.year}}</span>
        </li>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </ul>

    <video width="1440" height="900" data-src="{{ '/assets/video/fnih.mp4' | url }}" aria-label="Animated showreel, showcasing motion and designs from various projects over the years." muted playsinline loop></video>
  </div>
</section>